- Aluminum;
- Ardite;
- Chromium;
- Magnesium;
- Nickel;
- Platinum;
- Silver;
- Titanium;
- Zinc;
- Iridium;
- Tellurium;
- Tungsten;
- Uranium;
- Lead;

Alloys:
- CuprousTelluride;
- AlCu;
- CoCr;
- Iridoplatinum;
- MgAl;
- Stainless Steel;
- Steel;
- Sterling;
- TiAl;
- WCu;
- Rose Gold;

KubeJS:
- Kubejs works with event.custom() for:
   - alloyer multiblock;
   - sifter multiblock;
   - metal processing machine multiblock;
   - farm multiblock;
   - selling machine;
   - crushing machine;
   - smeltery multiblock.

Compressed blaze rod block:
- works like magma block but deals more damage.

Upgrading Station:
- In upgrading station you can upgrade your weapons. (More information in game with JEI/REI/EMI)

Money Command:
- /money give/remove/pay/set amount player

If you are interested about modification or modpack that's not yet released join discord: [Feed The Machine](https://discord.gg/P9JE4CxwdS)



You can use modification in your own modpack if you want.
This modification is only on curseforge and on modrinth.
